    <item>
      <title>Fifth Third 利润因费用收入大幅增长，因 Tricolor 破产而损失 1.78 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/fifth-third-profit-jumps-fee-income-records-178-million-loss-tricolor-bankruptcy-2025-10-17/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国地区银行 Fifth Third Bancorp 周五公布，由于手续费收入强劲，第三季度利润增长 14%，但因汽车经销商 Tricolor 破产而亏损 1.78 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/fifth-third-profit-jumps-fee-income-records-178-million-loss-tricolor-bankruptcy-2025-10-17/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 17 Oct 2025 11:24:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
